I-trachoma ingasuswa njengengxenye yezinkinga zezempilo zomphakathi ngokusebenzisa uhlelo i-SAFE, oluhlanganisa:
* Umshizo wokwelashwa kwe-trachomatous trichiasis, okuyisigaba esibangela ukulahleka kwamehlo yalesi sifo;
* Amakhambi athile (antibhayotiki) ukuze kususwe ukugugulela, ikakhulukazi ukunikezwa kwamakhambi kubantu abaningi, ikakhulukazi i-azithromycin, okunikezwa umkhiqizi ezinhlelweni zikazwelonke ngomkhakha i-International Trachoma Initiative;
* Ukuhlanzwa kwemfucuza; kanye
* Ukuthuthukiswa kwemvelo, ikakhulukazi ukutholakala okungcono kwamanzi namasango.
